    "name": "Beaming Stingray",
    "steam_appid": 2312490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/b3e2f45e40a0ecf98eb03185d2f82320.avif?t=1768249239\" width=800 height=374 /></span><br>索拉娅因一时冲动的复仇行为而命悬一线。在这款易于上手、流畅自如的飞行射击游戏中，与过去的自己并肩作战，找到回家的路。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与自己并肩作战</h2>通过吸收绿色时间子弹来填满索拉娅的时间之石，并与过去的自己一起战斗。对持盾敌人造成双倍伤害来暴露其弱点，或者与时间幻影一起共舞，创造出在线性时间中不可能实现的连击。借助前瞻性策略，叠加多个幻影，实现真正令人眼花缭乱的动作。充分利用时间之石的潜能是你成功和生存的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/2e290fc3ca37a91be6d2050ca3fcedb0.poster.avif?t=1768249239\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/2e290fc3ca37a91be6d2050ca3fcedb0.webm?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/2e290fc3ca37a91be6d2050ca3fcedb0.mp4?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >烧脑动作</h2>对抗复杂如谜的头目，将三个相同颜色/符号的敌人串联起来，获得分数加成的连击。在整个关卡中保持连击需要多次游戏会话、深思熟虑的策略和多幻影协调。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/276ce3069cf137cbb600050702a9b0f1.poster.avif?t=1768249239\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/276ce3069cf137cbb600050702a9b0f1.webm?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/276ce3069cf137cbb600050702a9b0f1.mp4?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >优雅而强力地飞翔</h2>在子弹墙之间冲刺和回击，消灭一波波坦克和战争机器。你操控的小神兽拥有独特的动作组合，能够激发创造力并造成快速伤害。近距离射击会造成双倍伤害，以回击结束连击将获得连击+、额外得分和时间之石强化。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/b7df30d7f700748ad4750b46f1929106.poster.avif?t=1768249239\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/b7df30d7f700748ad4750b46f1929106.webm?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/b7df30d7f700748ad4750b46f1929106.mp4?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救动物</h2>拉沙革命军(RRA)俘虏了这片土地上的许多神秘生物。想办法解救它们，它们或许会回报你的恩情。拯救所有动物将解锁索拉娅心中的一个秘密关卡和小游戏……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/bf83fc71cd302e67dd138bc445c314be.poster.avif?t=1768249239\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/bf83fc71cd302e67dd138bc445c314be.webm?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312490/extras/bf83fc71cd302e67dd138bc445c314be.mp4?t=1768249239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
